commits.content:
def Input():
    L=[]
    n=int(input('n='))
    for i in range(1,n+1):
        L+=[int(input())]
    return L
def Search(L):
    max=L.max()
    min=L.min()
    return max,min
def Output(max,min):
    print(f'{max} {min}')
max,min=Search(Input())
Output(max,min)
